    <item>
      <title>暴雨影响当地销售，中国将增加小麦库存</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/china-to-stockpile-more-wheat-as-heavy-rains-force-local-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于强降雨迫使一些农民将收获的小麦抛售到已经供不应求的市场上，中国政府正在加大对小麦的采购力度，以支撑当地价格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/china-to-stockpile-more-wheat-as-heavy-rains-force-local-sales</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 06:05:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Ninewide 称英国房价连续第三个月上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/uk-house-prices-rise-for-third-month-in-july-nationwide-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家顶级抵押贷款机构表示，英国房价连续第三个月上涨，进一步证明市场在 16 年来最高的借贷成本面前正在趋于稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/uk-house-prices-rise-for-third-month-in-july-nationwide-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 06:03:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Chanana：预计美元短期内将走弱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-01/chanana-expect-dollar-to-weaken-in-short-term-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[盛宝外汇策略主管 Charu Chanana 表示，美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔的鸽派言论为 9 月降息敞开了大门，但问题是美联储能降息到什么程度。她补充说，她预计美元今年将受到美联储和美国大选的影响而走弱。Charu Chanana 还在 Horizo​​ns Middle East and Africa 上与 Joumanna Bercetche 讨论了日元和英镑。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-01/chanana-expect-dollar-to-weaken-in-short-term-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 05:55:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>宝马盈利因中国主要市场需求疲软而下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/bmw-earnings-drop-on-waning-demand-in-key-china-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[宝马汽车公司 (BMW AG) 第二季度盈利出现下滑，原因是其主要市场中国销量下滑，这家德国公司加入了越来越多面临需求放缓困境的汽车制造商的行列。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/bmw-earnings-drop-on-waning-demand-in-key-china-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 05:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
