    <item>
      <title>日元贬值致日本出口商股价创 2020 年以来最大跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/japan-s-stocks-tumble-most-since-march-as-exporters-falls-on-yen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本股市下跌，东证指数在全线抛售中创下2020年4月以来的最大跌幅，因为日元大幅上涨给出口商带来压力，而央行加息拖累了房地产股。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/japan-s-stocks-tumble-most-since-march-as-exporters-falls-on-yen</guid>
